trans-unit.source: It works with MySQL, PostgreSQL, Oracle, SQL Server and SQLite and implements different locking strategies to handle concurrent access to the same session. Locking is necessary to prevent loss of data due to race conditions and to keep the session data consistent between read() and write(). With locking, requests for the same session will wait until the other one finished writing. For this reason it's best practice to close a session as early as possible to improve concurrency. PHPs internal files session handler also implements locking.
trans-unit.target: 它适用于MySQL、PostgreSQL、Oracle、SQL Server和SQLite,并实现了不同的锁定策略来处理对同一会话的并发访问。锁定是必要的,以防止由于竞赛条件造成的数据丢失,并在读()和写()之间保持会话数据的一致性。在锁定的情况下,对同一会话的请求会等到另一个会话完成写入。因此,最好的做法是尽早关闭会话以提高并发性。PHP的内部文件会话处理程序也实现了锁定。

trans-unit.source: Lock is the default implementation of the LockInterface.
LockAcquiringException is thrown when an issue happens during the acquisition of a lock.
trans-unit.target: 当锁的获取过程中发生问题时,会抛出LockAcquiringException。

trans-unit.source: LockConflictedException is thrown when a lock is acquired by someone else.
trans-unit.target: 当锁被别人获得时,会抛出LockConflictedException。

trans-unit.source: LockExpiredException is thrown when a lock may conflict due to a TTL expiration.
trans-unit.target: 当一个锁可能由于TTL过期而发生冲突时,会抛出LockExpiredException。

trans-unit.source: LockInterface defines an interface to manipulate the status of a lock.
trans-unit.target: LockInterface定义了一个用于操作锁的状态的接口。

trans-unit.source: LockReleasingException is thrown when an issue happens during the release of a lock.
trans-unit.target: 当锁的释放过程中发生问题时,就会抛出LockReleasingException。

trans-unit.source: LockStorageException is thrown when an issue happens during the manipulation of a lock in a store.
trans-unit.target: 当在商店中操作锁的过程中发生问题时,会抛出LockStorageException。

trans-unit.source: LockedException is thrown if the user account is locked.
trans-unit.target: 如果用户账户被锁定,则会抛出LockedException。

trans-unit.source: Locks a Request during the call to the backend.
trans-unit.target: 在调用后台时锁定请求。
